letState.ts):\n- `initialBalance: 1000` (SOL)\n- `autoConnect: false` (won't auto-connect even if localStorage has state)\n- `simulatedLatency: 500` (ms)\n- `persistState: true` (uses localStorage)\n\n### For Playwright Test Automation\n\n**To toggle connected state:**\n\n1. **Set to Connected:**\n   ```javascript\n   await page.evaluate(() => {\n     localStorage.setItem('rng-utopia-mock-wallet', JSON.stringify({\n       address: \"8PVb7MBvYSMfCq8d7nwPq4xvqV7x5gYqQKs6L9pRzJ2M\",\n       balance: 1000000000\n     }));\n   });\n   // Then reload page or trigger wallet connect flow\n   ```\n\n2. **Set to Disconnected:**\n   ```javascript\n   await page.evaluate(() => {\n     localStorage.removeItem('rng-utopia-mock-wallet');\n   });\n   ```\n\n**Important Notes:**\n- The component reads localStorage on mount via `loadPersistedState()` hook (lines 43-59)\n- Just setting localStorage is not enough - you may need to reload the page or call the `connect()` method\n- If `autoConnect: true` was configured on MockWalletProvider, it would auto-connect on mount\n- The `connecting` flag transitions to `true` during connection and `false` when complete (line 72, 96)\n- Balance persists in localStorage but is independent of connection state"}],"totalDurationMs":35185,"totalTokens":34062,"totalToolUseCount":18,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":233,"cache_read_input_tokens":32551,"output_tokens":1274,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":233,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
