{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BdriNpGmzEQBKS7M9B1vUS","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→import { Link, NavLink } from \"react-router-dom\";\n     2→import { useWallet, useBalance } from \"@rng-utopia/wallet/hooks\";\n     3→import { WalletButton } from \"@rng-utopia/ui\";\n     4→import { HeaderBossRaid, BossRaidModal, RNGBuffIndicator } from \"../../features/boss-raid\";\n     5→import { useQuests } from \"../../features/quests\";\n     6→\n     7→export function Header() {\n     8→  const { connected, connecting, address, connect, disconnect } = useWallet();\n     9→  const { formatted } = useBalance();\n    10→  const { unopenedChestCount, claimableQuestCount } = useQuests();\n    11→\n    12→  // Show yellow dot if there are unopened chests\n    13→  const hasUnopenedChests = unopenedChestCount > 0;\n    14→  // Show green dot if there are claimable quests\n    15→  const hasClaimableQuests = claimableQuestCount > 0;\n    16→\n    17→  return (\n    18→    <header className=\"header\">\n    19→      {/* Left: Logo */}\n    20→      <Link to=\"/\" className=\"header-logo\">\n    21→        <h1>RNG Wooftopia</h1>\n    22→      </Link>\n    23→\n    24→      {/* Center: Boss Raid + RNG Buff */}\n    25→      <div className=\"header-center\">\n    26→        <HeaderBossRaid />\n    27→        <RNGBuffIndicator />\n    28→      </div>\n    29→      <BossRaidModal />\n    30→\n    31→      {/* Right: Nav + Wallet */}\n    32→      <div className=\"header-right\">\n    33→        <nav>\n    34→          <NavLink to=\"/\" end>\n    35→            Games\n    36→          </NavLink>\n    37→          <NavLink to=\"/loot\" className={({ isActive }) => isActive ? \"active\" : \"\"}>\n    38→            Loot\n    39→            {hasUnopenedChests && <span className=\"nav-badge nav-badge--yellow\" />}\n    40→          </NavLink>\n    41→          <NavLink to=\"/quests\">\n    42→            Quests\n    43→            {hasClaimableQuests && <span className=\"nav-badge nav-badge--green\" />}\n    44→          </NavLink>\n    45→          <NavLink to=\"/fairness\">Fairness</NavLink>\n    46→          <NavLink to=\"/profile\">Profile</NavLink>\n    47→        </nav>\n    48→\n    49→        <WalletButton\n    50→          connected={connected}\n    51→          connecting={connecting}\n    52→          address={address}\n    53→          onConnect={connect}\n    54→          onDisconnect={disconnect}\n    55→          balance={formatted}\n    56→          showBalance={true}\n    57→        />\n    58→      </div>\n    59→    </header>\n    60→  );\n    61→}\n    62→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"abe33f0b-f1dd-4b96-a953-f5438b0c7570","uuid":"7245c020-eea7-4fa6-bbd8-1e87ba807c31","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/components/Header/Header.tsx","content":"import { Link, NavLink } from \"react-router-dom\";\nimport { useWallet, useBalance } from \"@rng-utopia/wallet/hooks\";\nimport { WalletButton } from \"@rng-utopia/ui\";\nimport { HeaderBossRaid, BossRaidModal, RNGBuffIndicator } from \"../../features/boss-raid\";\nimport { useQuests } from \"../../features/quests\";\n\nexport function Header() {\n  const { connected, connecting, address, connect, disconnect } = useWallet();\n  const { formatted } = useBalance();\n  const { unopenedChestCount, claimableQuestCount } = useQuests();\n\n  // Show yellow dot if there are unopened chests\n  const hasUnopenedChests = unopenedChestCount > 0;\n  // Show green dot if there are claimable quests\n  const hasClaimableQuests = claimableQuestCount > 0;\n\n  return (\n    <header className=\"header\">\n      {/* Left: Logo */}\n      <Link to=\"/\" className=\"header-logo\">\n        <h1>RNG Wooftopia</h1>\n      </Link>\n\n      {/* Center: Boss Raid + RNG Buff */}\n      <div className=\"header-center\">\n        <HeaderBossRaid />\n        <RNGBuffIndicator />\n      </div>\n      <BossRaidModal />\n\n      {/* Right: Nav + Wallet */}\n      <div className=\"header-right\">\n        <nav>\n          <NavLink to=\"/\" end>\n            Games\n          </NavLink>\n          <NavLink to=\"/loot\" className={({ isActive }) => isActive ? \"active\" : \"\"}>\n            Loot\n            {hasUnopenedChests && <span className=\"nav-badge nav-badge--yellow\" />}\n          </NavLink>\n          <NavLink to=\"/quests\">\n            Quests\n            {hasClaimableQuests && <span className=\"nav-badge nav-badge--green\" />}\n          </NavLink>\n          <NavLink to=\"/fairness\">Fairness</NavLink>\n          <NavLink to=\"/profile\">Profile</NavLink>\n        </nav>\n\n        <WalletButton\n          connected={connected}\n          connecting={connecting}\n          address={address}\n          onConnect={connect}\n          onDisconnect={disconnect}\n          balance={formatted}\n          showBalance={true}\n        />\n      </div>\n    </header>\n  );\n}\n","numLines":62,"startLine":1,"totalLines":62}}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_016pZXDTqkieYJfCzh2n8d3y","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I understand the full picture. Since `autoConnect: false`, the connected state requires actually clicking the connect button, or we need a smarter approach. For the visual test, the most reliable approach is:\n\n1. **Disconnected state**: Just navigate normally (default state, wallet not connected)\n2. **Connected state**: Navigate to the page, then click the connect wallet button and wait for the UI to update\n\nBut the connect flow has `simulatedLatency: 500ms` which could introduce timing issues. A better approach for determinism: use `addInitScript` to override the MockWalletProvider behavior by seeding localStorage AND patching the config to enable autoConnect.\n\nActually, the simplest and most robust approach: for connected state, navigate to the page and then programmatically call `connect()` via the button click. Let me check what the WalletButton looks like."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":893,"cache_read_input_tokens":52794,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":893},"output_tokens":5,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"abe33f0b-f1dd-4b96-a953-f5438b0c7570","uuid":"aa5df3a7-8dc7-4737-83d9-ceada4f9af91"}
